headline: Fastenal Company: Market Maybe Too Optimistic About Business Outlook
summary: Fastenal reported $1.825b in revenue, up 3.7% y/y, but fell slightly short of consensus expectations of $1.84b. Check out why I'm neutral about FAST stock.
